# Re-ignore runtime artifacts that accumulate under committed initiative
# directories.  ``!.megaplan/initiatives/**`` above un-ignores the entire
# initiative tree, but chain-state files, repair-queue markers, and any
# *.megaplan/* runtime scaffolding inside initiatives must stay ignored so
# they cannot dirty git_tracked launch preconditions.
.megaplan/initiatives/**/.megaplan/
.megaplan/initiatives/**/chain_state.json
.megaplan/initiatives/**/repair-queue/
!.megaplan/tickets/**
!.megaplan/ideas/
